{"_type":"issue","id":"TDF-tracker-9e7","title":"Stage-1 TT fantasy scoring badly off vs official — needs approach decision","description":"Our totals are jersey-bonus-only, far below official. Root causes: (1) stage-finish points missing — scorer reads 'ite' but first/latest stage only exposes 'itg'; (2) jersey bonuses awarded on classification rank even at 0 pts earned (spurious KOM bonus for Pogacar); (3) TT uses a compressed scale not in extracted rules; (4) back-marker official points (Verona 13@147th, Philipsen 9@177th) unexplained by public data; (5) Tissot time-guess (107 pts) is player-level, uncomputable. Decide: compute-approx w/ disclaimer vs authenticated official pull (SSO session) vs reposition fantasy as secondary.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","owner":"mattsnively@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-07-05T04:02:15Z","created_by":"Matt Snively","updated_at":"2026-07-05T18:22:05Z","closed_at":"2026-07-05T18:22:05Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":0,"comment_count":0}
